Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: New industrial condominium bays with main floor and mezzanine office development. Sale price recently reduced. The offering presents a rare turnkey opportunity for a variety of food preparation and retail sales uses. The sale price includes all existing food and sales related equipment. A complete list of items can be presented to any interested parties. Inquire with lead listing agent. Located in the developing Jacksonport Industrial District. Close proximity to major thoroughfares including Country Hills Blvd, Metis Trail and Deerfoot Trail NE. Complex has ample parking with 3.5 stalls per 1,000 SF of floor area. Site improvements include paved site, concrete curbing, sidewalks and landscaping. Unit is equipped with 200 amp power; HVAC for the entire building and two drive-in loading doors.

Owner-user/investment opportunity in a prime central Northeast location. The property is comprised of a 23,467 SF office/warehouse building, situated on 2.07 acres. Ability to occupy a portion of the building and hold the remainder as investment income.

Owner-user/investment opportunity in a prime central Northeast location. The property is comprised of a 23,467 SF office/warehouse building, situated on 2.07 acres. Ability to occupy a portion of the building and hold the remainder as investment income.

I-G (Industrial General) Zoning. High exposure site situated at 72 Avenue & 52 Street SE. 1.25 acres of fenced and secured loading and trailer parking area. High quality office finishing. Open office area, private offices, boardroom, meeting rooms, kitchen area & recreational room. State-of-the-art loading equipment on all dock doors.
OWNER-USER OR INVESTOR OPPORTUNITY: Rare opportunity to purchase an institutional, stand-alone distribution building with high quality office finishings and a large, fenced and secured yard

Office/Warehouse Industrial Condo for Sale. Various new interior upgrades completed in 2021. Built in 2006 this unit offers a good mix of office and warehouse space. Located in Eastfield Industrial Park with quick access to major thoroughfares including Peigan Trail, 52 Street SE, Barlow Trail and Deerfoot Trail SE. Six dedicated parking stalls. Office portion consists of six private offices, a boardroom, reception, washrooms and full kitchen on the second floor. LED lighting installed in warehouse. Make-up air unit existing (cfm TBV).

Quality office/warehouse space nicely built-out over two floors. Close proximity to Peigan Trail, Deerfoot Trail and Barlow Trail SE. 12 reserved parking stalls with additional street parking and parking at rear. Dock and drive-in loading. 3 walk-in freezer/coolers and a commercial kitchen in place. Condo fees, $1,068.11 per month.

Centrally located, standalone building. Highly desirable location with easy access to Blackfoot Trail, Glenmore Trail and Downtown Calgary. Generous parking and on-site storage. Dock and drive-in loading. Recently renovated open concept office space, LED lighting and ample window glazing along office area.
